dy provi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ed in that behalf, &amp; should all believers neglect this duty of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">yning to all particular congregations: it might follow therupon, that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1 word"> should h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">ve no visible political c<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="apex" EXTENT="1+ letters">rches upon earth,</P>
