<P>THe first subject of church powr, is eyther <HI>Supream,</HI> or <HI>Subordinat, &amp; Ministerial.</HI> the <HI>Supream</HI> (by way of gift from the father) is the Lord Iesus Christ, the <HI>Ministerial,</HI> is either extraordinary; as the <HI>Apostles, Prophets, &amp; Evangilists:</HI> or <HI>Ordinary;</HI> as every particular <HI>Congregational</HI> church.</P>
